<item>
            <title>[LU-19468] IPv6 conf-sanity test_5h: FAIL: client start failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19468</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for jianyu &amp;lt;yujian@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a45b8c6e-0e73-4bbf-a635-ec2876709509&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a45b8c6e-0e73-4bbf-a635-ec2876709509&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_5h failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Starting client: trevis-29vm1.trevis.whamcloud.com:  -o user_xattr,flock fd33:3981:3213:f020:0:5254:a2:6f9c@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
CMD: trevis-29vm1.trevis.whamcloud.com mkdir -p /mnt/lustre
CMD: trevis-29vm1.trevis.whamcloud.com mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,flock fd33:3981:3213:f020:0:5254:a2:6f9c@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
mount.lustre: mount fd33:3981:3213:f020:0:5254:a2:6f9c@tcp:/lustre at /mnt/lustre failed: Connection timed out
 conf-sanity test_5h: @@@@@@ FAIL: client start failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4657&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4657&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-570.42.2.el9_6.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4657&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master/4657&lt;/a&gt; - 5.14.0-570.42.2_lustre.el9.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;Please provide additional information about the failure here&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Console log on client:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[15977.367583] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: mkdir -p /mnt/lustre
[15977.382016] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,flock fd33:3981:3213:f020:0:5254:a2:6f9c@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
