[15990.886371] LustreError: 244831:0:(mgc_request.c:614:do_requeue()) failed processing log: -110
[16141.921281] LustreError: MGCfd33:3981:3213:f020:0:5254:a2:6f9c@tcp: Confguration from log lustre-client failed from MGS -110. Communication error between node &amp;amp; MGS, a bad configuration, or other errors. See syslog for more info
[16141.925254] Lustre: Unmounted lustre-client
